Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.01,0:02:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ozawa's fleet, now designated as a decoy unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,advancing from the Bungo Channel to the sea northeast of Manila no longer has any air cover. {the japanese lost 90% of their carrier-based planes in the battle of philippine sea, so now they had nothing to put on their carriers, therefore they decided to use them as a decoy}
